| --- | --- |

| **Geode-Kin · The Constructed Flesh** d10 · +2 Endurance +1 Acuity Fully organic but biologically resonant with Geode frequency — a classified Jade Empire engineering program several generations old. Geode Resonance (Geode-powered items work 1 tier higher), Construct Empathy, Enhanced Frame (+50% Frame Vitality pool). The Jade Empire considers you classified. Best for: organic-but-construct-adjacent, Gear-Forged cold war access. |  |
