### **Primal Jarl**

Primal Jarl · Alpha-aspected · Vitality Die: d12

**Core Mechanic:  **The Wrath State (replaces Rage)  Entering Wrath is not losing control — it is releasing the filter that normally stands between the character's will and the full force of their Aetheric nature. As an Instinct, enter the Wrath State for up to 1 minute. Uses per Deep Attunement: 2 (increases to 3 at Depth 6, 4 at Depth 12, unlimited at Depth 17). While in Wrath State: Resonant Fortune on Forcefulness Active Resonances and Warding Resonances; +2 to melee damage (increases to +3 at Depth 9, +4 at Depth 16); resistance to slashing, piercing, and bludgeoning damage from non-magical sources; cannot enact Workings or use Weaving abilities — the Aetheric field is fully physical. Wrath ends if the character hasn't attacked or taken damage since their last Moment, or if they choose to end it. After W

