### **Callings**

**Oath of the Solar Compact**  —  Devotion

Tenets: Honesty. Courage. Compassion for the weak. Duty to the Solar Throne's ideals (if not its current holder).

**Sacred Weapons (Depth 3):  **As an Instinct, infuse one weapon with Oath-light for 1 minute. It deals +1d4 radiant damage, sheds bright light in 20 ft, and counts as Sun-Kissed Adamas for the purpose of affecting undead.

Turn Void-Husks (Depth 3, Aetheric Benediction): All Void-Husks within 30 ft that can see or hear you must make a Resonance Warding Resonance (Threshold = 8 + Mastery + Resonance) or be unable to willingly move toward you for 1 minute.

**Oath Aura (Depth 7):  **Allies in your Aura of Oath are immune to Dread-Struck and have Resonant Fortune on all Active Resonances made to resist Soul-Swayed.

**Oath of the Loom****'****s Justice**  —  Vengeance

Tenets: Fight the greater evil. No mercy for those who prey on the innocent. By any means necessary — the Loom measures results.

**Vow of Enmity (Depth 3):  **As an Instinct, declare one creature your Quarry. For 1 minute: Resonant Fortune on all Strike Resonances against the Quarry; if the Quarry dies, you may immediately designate a new Quarry as a free action.

Loom-Pull Step (Depth 3, Aetheric Benediction): Teleport up to 30 ft to a space adjacent to your Quarry as an Instinct — the Loom pulls the thread tight.

**Relentless Pursuit (Depth 7):  **Your movement is not impeded by difficult terrain when moving toward your Quarry. If your Quarry becomes Aether-Veiled, you can still perceive their general location within 30 ft.

**Oath of Ancient Sideros**  —  Ancients

Tenets: Protect the light of the zodiac. Preserve life — mortal, divine, and Legendary Beast. The beauty of the living world is worth dying for.

Nature's Wrath (Depth 3, Aetheric Benediction): Spectral vines erupt around all hostile creatures within 10 ft — Forcefulness Warding Resonance (Threshold = 8 + Mastery + Resonance) or Resonance-Locked until the start of your next Moment.

**Aura of Warding (Depth 7):  **Allies in your Aura of Oath gain resistance to damage from Workings — halve all Working damage taken.

**Legendary Beast Accord (Depth 15):  **You have established a covenant with all Legendary Beasts. They will not attack you unprovoked. You may request one audience with any Beast per year — they will receive you, though they are not obligated to help.

### **Void-Hunter**

Void-Hunter · Beta-aspected · Vitality Die: d10

**Core Mechanic:  **Void Quarry  As an Instinct, designate one creature as your Void Quarry. This designation lasts until the creature is dead or until you designate a new Quarry (only one at a time, no cost to switch after a kill). Against Void Quarry: +1d6 damage on all Strike Resonances; Resonant Fortune on Attunement Active Resonances to track, perceive, or gather information about the Quarry; always know the Quarry's direction and approximate distance (within 1 mile) as long as you have seen them in the last 24 hours. Void Quarry — Coil Specialization: Against Void-Husks, Coil operatives, and creatures with active Lead-Scale Corruption, the bonus damage increases to +1d8 and you know the target's current Corruption Gauge level on sight. You have studied this enemy

