| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | +2 | RES mod (min 2) | Fate Number Reading (Instinct, 30 ft), Fate-Knot Weaving, half-caster Channels begin |
| 2 | +2 | RES mod | Calling chosen (Loom's Hand / The Unwritten / Star-Reader), Calling D2 features |
| **3** | +2 | RES mod | Calling chosen, Bond Cartography (read two Fate Numbers simultaneously to see Bond tier/health) |
| **4** | +2 | RES mod | Attribute Score Improvement, Zodiac Attunement (after Legendary Beast encounter), — |
| **5** | +3 | RES mod | Probability Threading (spend 2 same-type Knots for enhanced effect: +5 bonus or auto-crit) |
| 6 | +3 | RES mod | Calling D6 features |
| 7 | +3 | RES mod | Loom Sight (1×/Deep: 10-min read; learn approaching Fate thresholds in area) |
| 8 | +3 | RES mod | Attribute Score Improvement, — |
| **9** | +4 | RES+MB | Fate-Knot Expansion: pool → RES mod + MB; own rolls also generate Knots; Knots no longer auto-release |
| 10 | +4 | RES+MB | Calling D10 features |
