**Misuse and the Stillness:** Within Aether-Dampening Ore zones (The Stillness), Apex Fragment Reagents become inert — they cannot be activated by any Weaving, and any attempt to do so wastes the fragment without effect. Carry them through such zones with caution.

**Storage:** Apex Fragments may be safely stored only in cured Hearthwood vessels, sealed Resonant Geode caskets, or Kanya Siddha purification linen. Lesser containers permit slow Aetheric leak — a fragment kept in an ordinary pouch may degrade from T4 to T3 over the course of a season, and so on downward.

### **Aetheric Channels -- Weaving Reference**

Full-caster Paths: Comet-Magus, Zodiac Priest, Resonance Seeker, Primal Accord. Half-caster: Oathed Vanguard, Scion-Pledged, Void-Hunter, Geode-Pilot, Coil-Stalker, Fade-Guardian. Quarter-caster: Fate-Breaker. Special: Star-Born (Surge Points = Depth), Ashé-Medium (Ashé Vessel), Rāśi-Siddha (Tapas), Accord-Maker (Infusions/Blueprints).

| **Depth** | **1st** | **2nd** | **3rd** | **4th** | **5th** | **6th** | **7th** | **8th** | **9th** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **1** | 2 | — | — | — | — | — | — | — | — |
| **2** | 3 | — | — | — | — | — | — | — | — |
