| **Lesser Restoration** | 40 gm | Ashélands Iyanifa (30 gm) | Khem-Ma'at (75 gm) |
| **Aetheric Examination (Identify equiv.)** | 20 gm | Comet-Magus Conclave (free if registered) | Independent (40 gm) |
| **Detect Magic (Aetheric Sight)** | 15 gm | Most temples (10 gm) | Order of Pure Reason (refuses on principle) |
| **Greater Restoration** | 100 gm | Kanya-Siddha (80 gm) | Khem-Ma'at (200 gm) |
| **Raise from Loom-Tested** (Revivify equiv.) | 300 gm + ritual component | Kanya-Siddha (250 gm) | Khem-Ma'at (500 gm) |
| **Raise Dead** | 1,000 gm + 500 gm reagent | Twin Dream-Fish Veil-Walker (special) | Khem-Ma'at Sun-Forge (2,000 gm) |
| **True Resurrection** | 25,000 gm + 25,000 gm reagent | Apex-Emanation gated; not for sale | — |
| **Remove Lead-Scale (Kanya purification)** | 50 gm/session (4 stacks per session) | Kanya-Siddha only | Not available outside the tradition |
| **Speak with Dead** | 50 gm + offering | Ashélands Babalawo (45 gm) | Tuathan veil-walker (200 gm — Otherworld access fee) |
| **Sending (long-distance message)** | 25 gm | Resonance Seeker (15 gm) | Comet-Magus (75 gm — registers the message) |

### **Cultural surcharges and refusals:**

- The **Order of Pure Reason** refuses all Working Casting Services on principle. They will sell Aether-Dampening Ore at high markup instead.

- The **Khem-Ma****'****at Solar Throne** charges premium prices but works only for those of appropriate moral character (Game Master adjudicates).

- The **Kanya-Siddha** are the cheapest healing source in the world. The Bee-Priestess oversees the price structure; she has held it stable for 200 years deliberately, against constant pressure to raise rates.

- **Comet-Magi** will register any Working they cast in the Conclave's records. Some requests are therefore politically expensive even when the Marks cost is reasonable.

- **Aethar****'****s faction** offers Working services at rates that are too low. This is the recruitment vector. Decline politely.

**APPENDIX**

World Reference

Disciplines Reference  ·  All 17 skills with governing attributes       and all Resonance Thresholds (Simple 8 through Void-Touched 30)

General Feats  ·  20 feats available at ASI Depths (4, 8, 12, 16, 19)

Adventuring Rules  ·  Travel pace, light & vision, falling, hazards

Languages  ·  11 world languages with speakers and scripts

