| **Cook****'****s utensils** | 1 gm | Prepare meals that improve Endurance Warding (Resonant Fortune for next 24 hr if cooked at Mastered Active Resonance DT 14), identify poisons |
| **Glassblower****'****s tools** | 30 gm | Create glass vessels, fit Noctilith lenses, identify glass origin/quality |
