| **Mason****'****s tools** | 10 gm | Identify stonework origin, detect hidden compartments, set stone-based traps |
| **Painter****'****s supplies** | 10 gm | Identify artistic style, forge artworks, decode Resonant Cartographer's hidden notation |
| **Potter****'****s tools** | 10 gm | Make vessels suitable for Apex Fragment storage (with proper materials), identify pot-marks |
| **Smith****'****s tools** | 20 gm | Identify metal origin, make/repair weapons and armor, apply Anointments (with cultural lineage), recognize cultural smith marks |
