| **Woodcarver****'****s tools** | 1 gm | Make/repair arrows and bows, carve ritual objects, identify wood origin |

### **Other Tools:**

| **Tool** | **Cost** | **Active Resonance Enables** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Disguise Kit** | 25 gm | Alter appearance to pass as another person (RES Active Resonance vs. observer's ACU). Lasts until disturbed or worn off (8 hours). |
