**Gaming Sets** (each: 1 gm; weight negligible) — Mastery enables reading opponents (Insight Resonant Fortune in social settings), recognizing cheats, and identifying regional/cultural variants. Sideros gaming sets include: **Dragon****'****s Eye** (dice; Duchy Compact taverns), **Zodiac Cards** (strategy cards; Kallos-Sworn use these), **Orisha Tiles** (Ashélands board game), **Jade Empire chess** (Shen-lì), **Moana-kin shell-toss** (divination/game hybrid).

**Musical Instruments** (cost varies — Drum 6 gm / Flute 2 gm / Horn 3 gm / Lute 35 gm / Lyre 30 gm / Viol 30 gm / Bagpipes 30 gm / Bone-flute (Te Kapo) 8 gm / Hand drum (Ashélands) 5 gm / Sitar (Jade Empire) 40 gm) — Mastery enables performance for income (5 sm to 5 gm per hour depending on quality), bardic-style inspiration if Path supports, and cultural recognition by audiences from the instrument's origin.

