| **Void-Sight Lens (Te Kapo)** | 150 gm | Te Kapo-crafted void-glass lens. Grants Void-Sense (60 ft) for 10 minutes on activation; 3 charges per lens. Charges restore on Deep Attunement under a moonless sky. Outside the Te Kapo homeland, may be confiscated by suspicious authorities. |
| **Beast Resonance Tuner** | 120 gm | Small Beast-cultural smith's instrument. Detects active Beast Resonance fields within 30 ft and reads the holder's current Resonance Pool levels for any encountered Beast. Required for some Beast-Bound Anointment work. |
