### **QUICK REFERENCE**

Sideros Reference  |  Page XVIII

| **✶  ****CORE TERMINOLOGY****  ✶** **SIDEROS TERM** **MEANING** **Resonance Depth**  Character Level **Mastery Bonus**  Proficiency Bonus **Vitality**  Hit Points **Guard Rating**  Armour Class **Pulse Order**  Initiative **Active Resonance**  Skill Check / Attack Roll **Warding Resonance**  Saving Throw **Discipline**  Skill **Aetheric Channels**  Spell Slots **Working**  Spell **Weaving**  Casting Magic **Instinct**  Bonus Action **Resonant Fortune**  Advantage **Resonant Discord**  Disadvantage **Brief Attunement**  Short Rest **Deep Attunement**  Long Rest **Fated Bond**  NPC Relationship **Kindred / Path / Calling**  Race / Class / Subclass **✶  ****ATTRIBUTES****  ✶** **ABBR.** **ATTRIBUTE** **GOVERNS** **FOR** **Forcefulness**  Strength, physical force, intimidation **SWI** **Swiftness**  Dexterity, speed, finesse **END** **Endurance**  Constitution, resilience, fortitude **ACU** **Acuity**  Intelligence, knowledge, investigation **ATT** **Attunement**  Wisdom, perception, empathy **RES** **Resonance**  Charisma, force of fate, social | **✶  ****CORE FORMULAS****  ✶** **FORMULA** **CALCULATION** **Active Resonance**  d20 + Attr mod + Mastery Bonus (if Mastered) **Warding Resonance**  d20 + Attr mod (+ MB if Path grants Mastery) **Strike Resonance**  d20 + Attr mod + MB  vs.  target Guard Rating **Pulse Order**  d20 + Swiftness modifier  (resets each Pulse) **Guard Rating (standard)**  10 + SWI modifier + armor bonus **Guard Rating (Siddha)**  10 + ATT modifier + MB  (full Tapas pool) **Guard Rating (Gear-Forged)**  10 + END modifier **Ambient Attunement**  10 + ATT modifier + MB (if Perception Mastered) **Working Threshold DC**  8 + Mastery Bonus + Weaving Attribute modifier **Working Strike Bonus**  Mastery Bonus + Weaving Attribute modifier **Vitality at D1**  Roll Vita Die + END modifier (minimum 1) **Vitality per Depth**  Roll Vita Die + END modifier; add to total **✶  ****DIFFICULTY THRESHOLDS (DT)****  ✶** **5**  Easy **10**  Moderate **15**  Hard **20**  Very Hard **25**  Nearly Impossible **30** **✶  ****ACTION ECONOMY****  ✶** **Act:**  Primary Act per Moment — Strike, Weave, Grapple, Dash, Use Item, Help **Instinct:**  Secondary action per Moment — Path Instinct features, minor actions **Reflex:**  Triggered response; once per Pulse; occurs off your Moment **Movement:**  Up to Speed in feet; can split around Acts. Not an action. **Free Interaction:**  Drop item, speak, or minor object interaction — no cost **✶  ****RESONANT STRIKE ****&**** MISS****  ✶** Resonant Strike (nat 20): Roll all damage dice twice. A natural 20 is always a hit. Critical Miss (nat 1): Always fails. Game Master may add complication. **✶  ****FORTUNE ****&**** DISCORD****  ✶** **Resonant Fortune:**  Roll 2d20, take the higher result **Resonant Discord:**  Roll 2d20, take the lower result **✶  ****WARDING RESONANCE ATTRIBUTE MAPPING****  ✶** **ATTRIBUTE** **USED AGAINST** **Forcefulness (FOR)**  Physical force, being knocked back, crushing effects **Swiftness (SWI)**  Explosions, breath weapons, area effects (can be dodged) **Endurance (END)**  Poison, disease, exhaustion, death effects, constitution **Acuity (ACU)**  Illusions, mind-affecting effects requiring logical resistance **Attunement (ATT)**  Charms, scrying, emotional manipulation, Aetheric influence **Resonance (RES)**  Fear, social coercion, Fated Bond contests, Void corruption **✶  ****WEAPON MASTERY****  ✶** **Mastered**  Full Mastery Bonus on Strike Resonance attack AND damage **Half-Mastered**  Half Mastery Bonus (rounded down) on attack rolls only **Unmastered**  Resonant Discord (2d20 lower) on ALL Strike Resonances **Armor (no Mastery)**  Resonant Discord on all FOR + SWI Active Resonances & Wardings **✶  ****SUSTAINED RESONANCE (CONCENTRATION)****  ✶** One Sustained Working at a time (Gemini Attunement: two). When you take damage while sustaining, make an END Warding Resonance (DC 10 or half damage, whichever is higher). Fail = Working ends. Drops if unconscious. End freely as a Free Interaction. **✶  ****THE STILLNESS (AETHER-DAMPENING ORE)****  ✶** **Weave-capable**  Resonance-Locked — cannot Weave any Working inside the zone **Aetheric Artifacts**  Suppressed — magical bonuses inactive **Black Iron weapons**  Unaffected — retain full effectiveness in Stillness zones **Gear-Forged (Tier I Geode)**  Fully suppressed. Tier III+: 50% capacity **Detection**  Weave-capable feel it before entering (ATT check DC 12) **Range (Refined Ore)**  30 ft radius per unit; 60 ft Dunmarim-processed; stacks **✶  ****CONDITIONS QUICK REF****  ✶** **Sight-Severed**  Discord on sight attacks; foes have Fortune to hit you **Dread-Struck**  Discord all rolls while source visible; cannot move toward it **Grappled**  Speed 0; escape as Act (FOR/SWI contest vs grappler) **Seized**  Speed 0 and cannot increase (Restrained equivalent) **Incapacitated**  Cannot take Acts or Instincts; drops Sustained Resonances **Soul-Swayed**  Treats source as trusted ally; cannot Strike Resonate it **Loom-Suspended**  Unconscious (stable); auto-fail FOR/SWI; attacks have Fortune **Loom-Tested**  Dying at 0 Vitality; d20 DC 10 each Moment; 3 failures = thread ends **Corrupted**  1d6 dmg/Moment; Discord attacks & checks; END Warding to end **Prone**  Discord vs. ranged; melee foes have Fortune; stand = half Speed **Dazed**  Discord all Resonances until start of your next Moment **Resonance-Locked**  Cannot Weave or use Channel abilities (Ore zone or source) **Aetheric Depletion**  L1-5: Discord → half dmg → no Workings → 1d10/Moment. Clears on Deep Attunement **Void-Touched Exposure**  Per stack: Discord Insight; 3+ stacks: Core intrusive thoughts **Exhausted**  L1: Discord checks / L2: Speed halved / L4: Max Vita halved / L6: Thread ends |
| --- | --- |

