### **THE WORLD OF SIDEROS**

World Primer  |  Page XX  |  For Players

| **✶  ****THE WORLD OF SIDEROS****  ✶** Sideros is in its fourth era — the Shattered Age. The twelve gods of the Pantheonic Council fell when Ophiuchus was corrupted by the Hollow Serpent and shattered. The remaining twelve gods chose to dissolve themselves into vast Aetheric presences rather than dissolve entirely: they became the Legendary Beasts. They no longer govern — but they remember, and they recognize mortals whose soul-frequency resonates with their domain. **✶  ****THE LOOM OF FATE****  ✶** The Loom is a cosmic structure predating every civilization. It weaves probable futures from the Aether. Every creature has a Fate Number (1d100, permanent) marking their position in the Loom's pattern. Numbers that fall near each other are drawn toward Fated Bond relationships. Numbers near 13, 66, or 99 carry the Hollow Serpent's resonance. The primary antagonist, Aethar the Serpent Bearer, intends to destroy the Loom entirely. **✶  ****KEY FACTIONS****  ✶** **Ashen Coil**  Aethar’s organization. Publicly: trade syndicate & academic society. Privately: structured intelligence operation pursuing the Five Stages. Three layers: outer-ring agents (unknowing), inner-ring operatives (partial knowledge), Triad (full knowledge). Produces Void-Husks, controls Ore supply, tracks bond lineages to prevent the Quint Bond. **Kallos-Sworn**  The twelve-house order preventing another Pantheonic catastrophe. Each house corresponds to a zodiac sign and a Legendary Beast. Centuries-long intelligence war against the Coil. Their institutional memory is primarily Beta. Arch-Oracle Lyra has calculated the Loom seal’s failure timeline. **Three Conclaves**  The world’s three Weaving scholarly organizations. Their combined Aetheric pressure is the only thing keeping the Crystalline Core sealed. Shifting Horizons (Aethar’s former Conclave), Earthly Core, and Veil-Walkers. Destabilizing them is Aethar’s Stage 1 objective. **Loom of Fate org.**  A Beta organization — patient, networked, invisible. Weaves fate at an institutional level. Fated Bonds form between souls in resonance regardless of alignment. The Ashen Coil’s internal bond is genuine, real, and one of the reasons they’re dangerous. **Order of Pure Reason**  Dunmarim-affiliated. Anti-Aetheric ideology. Controls Aether-Dampening Ore production. Banned Weep-Stone import. Active conflict with the Coil over Ore supply chain control. **✶  ****THE QUINT BOND PROPHECY****  ✶** **"**  the Five Who Remember What the Gods Were. **"**  Serath has identified 3 of 5 and withheld this information from Aethar for six weeks. The Fang of the Whisper’s true secondary mission is to prevent these five from ever occupying the same location simultaneously. | **✶  ****LEGENDARY BEASTS ****&**** ZODIAC SIGNS****  ✶** **SIGN** **LEGENDARY BEAST** **DOMAIN** **Aries**  Ashen Ram Fire / Initiative **Taurus**  Khalkotauros Earth / Endurance **Gemini**  Twin-Serpents Air / Duality **Cancer**  Adamant Crab Water / Protection **Leo**  Nemean Lion Fire / Glory **Virgo**  Queen Bee Earth / Healing **Libra**  Great Roc Air / Balance **Scorpio**  Stygian Scorpion Water / Secrets **Sagittarius**  Star-Metal Stag Fire / Stars **Capricorn**  Sea-Goat Earth / Mastery **Aquarius**  Kelp-Weaver Water / Networks **Pisces**  Twin Dream-Fish Water / Dreams **Ophiuchus** **✶  ****FATED BOND FORMATION — THREE STAGES****  ✶** **Stage 1: Resonant Proximity**  Passive and unconscious. Numbers near each other produce sharpened attention, unusual clarity. No mechanical benefit — narrative weight only. Stellar Cartographers can detect it. **Stage 2: The Kindle Moment**  The Loom decides when — a shared moment of genuine significance: near-death, revelation, witnessed grief. Cannot be manufactured. The bond cannot form without it. **Stage 3: Acknowledgment**  Both parties consciously name and accept the bond. A formal ceremony is available (1 day, no cost). Advances the bond to the next tier. A Denied Bond traps both in mounting instability. **✶  ****SESSION ZERO QUESTIONS****  ✶** **What do you want?** **What have you lost?** **What does the Loom want with you?** **What do you know about the Ashen Coil?** **Who would notice if you disappeared?** |
| --- | --- |

