### **Faction NPC Templates**

Quick stat-block references for the six factions a campaign repeatedly encounters. Each tier is appropriate for parties at the indicated Depth range. Use these as starting points and customize.

### **Coil Operative**

| **Tier** | **Depth** | **Vitality** | **GR** | **Mastery Bonus** | **Key Abilities** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Recruit** | 3 | 22 | 13 | +2 | Lead-Trace dagger (1d4 piercing + 1 Lead-Scale on hit). Stealthy; flees if outmatched. |
| **Agent** | 8 | 65 | 15 | +3 | Anointed weapon (Lead-Suppressed). Cast 1 Working (Disguise Self or Charm). Knows operational dead-drops. |
| **Handler** | 15 | 120 | 17 | +5 | Multiple Workings. Carries a small Void-Touched Crystal cache. Loyal to one of the Triad personally. |

### **Kallos-Sworn Observer**

| **Tier** | **Depth** | **Vitality** | **GR** | **Mastery Bonus** | **Key Abilities** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Initiate** | 3 | 28 | 14 | +2 | Formulation Ledger; 2 basic Workings; records all encounters meticulously. Pacifist unless directly threatened. |
| **Sworn** | 8 | 70 | 15 | +3 | 4-5 Workings including detection. Aetheric Examination at-will. Recognises Coil agents at sight. |
| **Senior** | 15 | 130 | 16 | +5 | 7+ Workings; controls one Resonant Binding component if relevant; has Conclave authority. |

