| **Cell Leader** | 8 | 55 | 15 | +3 | Network of 3-5 Whispers; access to safe houses; one anointed dagger (Bog-Etched typically). |
| **Director** | 15 | 110 | 16 | +5 | Reports directly to Drava Nullsong; can call in regional resources; carries one Apex Fragment for emergency use. |

